17
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:03,080
And here's the golden rule for our
mission, the most important part.

18
00:01:03,080 --> 00:01:06,320
The first step is always to ask about the
other person.

19
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:09,120
People love to talk about what they like
